import React from 'react';
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom';
import Grid from '@material-ui/core/Grid';

export default props =>
    <grid Container> //grid must be a container or at least have child element(s) grid items
        <grid item sm>
            Menu pane
        </grid>

        <grid item sm>
            Cart pane
        </grid>
    </grid>
